HEADWORD: Interlapse
<hw>In"ter*lapse`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>inter-</ets> + <ets>lapse</ets>: cf. L. <ets>interlabi</ets>,
